description: Visually inspect panel for signs of overheating, corrosion, or damage.

description: Test panel grounding and bonding connections.
Test all GFCI breakers and receptacles for proper operation.
Inspect all breakers for signs of wear or damage.
Replace panel at end of service life or if failed.
